WEBVTT

1
00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:20.000
<b><font face="Gill Sans MT Condensed" color="#80ff00">jmg subs</font></b>

2
00:00:50.551 --> 00:00:53.251
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(CONVERSING IN FINNISH)</b></font>

3
00:01:21.548 --> 00:01:22.814
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(DOOR CLOSING)</b></font>

4
00:02:13.901 --> 00:02:15.400
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(GROANS)</b></font>

5
00:02:46.833 --> 00:02:48.633
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Helsinki. one hour. Senator.</b></font>

6
00:02:51.271 --> 00:02:52.704
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Is POTUS up and about yet?</b></font>

7
00:02:52.706 --> 00:02:54.639
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>POTUS status unknown. sir.</b></font>

8
00:02:54.641 --> 00:02:56.341
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Actually. I heard him
moving around just now.</b></font>

9
00:02:56.343 --> 00:02:57.776
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I think he's awake. sir.</b></font>

10
00:02:57.778 --> 00:02:59.377
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- (KNOCKING AT DOOR)
- Enter.</b></font>

11
00:03:01.848 --> 00:03:02.948
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Morris.</b></font>

12
00:03:02.950 --> 00:03:04.349
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Good morning.</b></font>

13
00:03:04.351 --> 00:03:05.351
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Mr. President. sir.</b></font>

14
00:03:06.920 --> 00:03:08.853
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SIGHS)</b></font>

15
00:03:08.855 --> 00:03:10.789
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Well. here we go again.</b></font>

16
00:03:10.791 --> 00:03:13.291
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Twenty points down
in the polls.</b></font>

17
00:03:13.293 --> 00:03:16.328
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Friends and enemies lining up
to stab me in the back.</b></font>

18
00:03:17.998 --> 00:03:19.698
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Well. at least
you're still in my corner.</b></font>

19
00:03:19.700 --> 00:03:20.899
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Right. Morris?</b></font>

20
00:03:21.335 --> 00:03:22.567
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(CHUCKLES)</b></font>

21
00:03:26.506 --> 00:03:28.940
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Come on. you're not gonna tell
the first lady. are you?</b></font>

22
00:03:28.942 --> 00:03:30.822
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Wheels down in Helsinki
in an hour. sir.</b></font>

23
00:03:31.645 --> 00:03:33.778
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(GROANS)
I'd rather take a bullet</b></font>

24
00:03:33.780 --> 00:03:36.248
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>than go through another one
of these conferences.</b></font>

25
00:03:37.317 --> 00:03:38.683
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SIGHS)</b></font>

26
00:03:38.685 --> 00:03:40.885
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>That was insensitive.</b></font>

27
00:03:40.887 --> 00:03:44.789
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Saying something like that to a man
who actually took a bullet for me.</b></font>

28
00:03:44.791 --> 00:03:48.627
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Well. a near-death experience does change
one's prospective on a few things. sir.</b></font>

29
00:03:48.629 --> 00:03:50.528
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Look. Morris. I'm really sorry</b></font>

30
00:03:50.530 --> 00:03:52.764
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm forcing you
to retire after this trip.</b></font>

31
00:03:52.766 --> 00:03:53.806
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I know how you feel.</b></font>

32
00:03:58.405 --> 00:04:01.245
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Mr. President. sir. one thing
I have learned is that...</b></font>

33
00:04:02.809 --> 00:04:04.542
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>...life is just too damn short</b></font>

34
00:04:04.544 --> 00:04:06.645
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>not to have a cookie
when you want one.</b></font>

35
00:04:08.515 --> 00:04:09.681
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>See you in a half?</b></font>

36
00:05:37.471 --> 00:05:39.637
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>MAN: Welcome
to Lapland. gentlemen.</b></font>

37
00:05:39.639 --> 00:05:41.773
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>A real hunting paradise.</b></font>

38
00:05:41.775 --> 00:05:44.743
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We've got moose.
We've got bears.</b></font>

39
00:05:44.745 --> 00:05:47.545
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We've got wolves. lynx.</b></font>

40
00:05:47.547 --> 00:05:49.647
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Everything in here.</b></font>

41
00:05:49.649 --> 00:05:52.417
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>So. what kind of game
are you looking for?</b></font>

42
00:05:53.854 --> 00:05:56.121
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Big game.
- MAN: Roger. sir.</b></font>

43
00:05:56.123 --> 00:05:59.624
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're gonna get it.
I promise.</b></font>

44
00:05:59.626 --> 00:06:03.595
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- (BEEPING)
- Great. Land the helicopter.</b></font>

45
00:06:03.597 --> 00:06:06.664
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We haven't the license
to hunt here on this area.</b></font>

46
00:06:06.666 --> 00:06:08.066
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Just execute my order.</b></font>

47
00:06:08.769 --> 00:06:10.101
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Roger. sir.</b></font>

48
00:06:11.471 --> 00:06:12.871
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(WHISPERS IN FINNISH)</b></font>

49
00:07:02.889 --> 00:07:05.757
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Never seen
a hunting team like this.</b></font>

50
00:07:05.759 --> 00:07:07.091
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I expect not.</b></font>

51
00:07:10.030 --> 00:07:11.796
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What you got there?</b></font>

52
00:07:11.798 --> 00:07:13.465
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Something like scope?</b></font>

53
00:07:15.802 --> 00:07:18.002
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It's a targeting system.</b></font>

54
00:07:18.004 --> 00:07:19.571
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Targeting system? What for?</b></font>

55
00:07:20.474 --> 00:07:21.973
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Right.</b></font>

56
00:07:21.975 --> 00:07:24.642
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Shoulder-mounted. Chinese
FN-6 surface-to-air missile.</b></font>

57
00:07:24.644 --> 00:07:27.512
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Not the most advanced SAM
on the market by any means.</b></font>

58
00:07:27.514 --> 00:07:30.849
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>but more than capable of
taking out passenger aircraft.</b></font>

59
00:07:30.851 --> 00:07:32.984
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Passenger aircraft?
What do you mean?</b></font>

60
00:07:32.986 --> 00:07:34.786
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>A civilian aircraft.
I should say.</b></font>

61
00:07:36.823 --> 00:07:39.023
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>With a state-of-the-art
military grade aircraft.</b></font>

62
00:07:39.025 --> 00:07:41.559
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>the defense systems
would most likely deflect</b></font>

63
00:07:41.561 --> 00:07:42.760
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>the attack.</b></font>

64
00:07:42.762 --> 00:07:44.496
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Unless. that is...</b></font>

65
00:07:45.832 --> 00:07:48.199
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The defense systems
had somehow been disabled.</b></font>

66
00:07:49.169 --> 00:07:50.268
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(CHUCKLES NERVOUSLY)</b></font>

67
00:07:51.638 --> 00:07:53.538
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Are you...</b></font>

68
00:07:53.540 --> 00:07:55.640
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Are you terrorists?</b></font>

69
00:07:55.642 --> 00:07:58.142
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(CHUCKLES)</b></font>

70
00:07:58.144 --> 00:08:00.845
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You certainly look terrified.
so I suppose we must be.</b></font>

71
00:08:00.847 --> 00:08:02.514
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(INHALES DEEPLY)</b></font>

72
00:08:04.885 --> 00:08:07.646
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But I don't think you should
be worrying about us.</b></font>

73
00:08:08.722 --> 00:08:11.789
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You should be
worrying about yourself.</b></font>

74
00:08:11.791 --> 00:08:13.911
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>In fact. in my opinion.
you should be running.</b></font>

75
00:08:14.928 --> 00:08:17.061
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Running?
- HAZAR: Absolutely.</b></font>

76
00:08:17.063 --> 00:08:18.596
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You see. I intend to kill you.</b></font>

77
00:08:18.598 --> 00:08:21.099
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You have no way
of overpowering me.</b></font>

78
00:08:21.101 --> 00:08:22.901
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>but I don't yet have
a weapon in my hand.</b></font>

79
00:08:22.903 --> 00:08:24.969
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>so your best chance is to run.</b></font>

80
00:08:24.971 --> 00:08:26.104
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(CHUCKLES NERVOUSLY)</b></font>

81
00:08:26.673 --> 00:08:28.072
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Like this.</b></font>

82
00:08:52.832 --> 00:08:53.965
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(BEEPING)</b></font>

83
00:09:31.037 --> 00:09:33.237
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>MAN: (ON TAPE) ABC of Hunting.</b></font>

84
00:09:33.239 --> 00:09:35.907
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Volume Four. for Beginners.</b></font>

85
00:09:35.909 --> 00:09:38.810
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Attracting deer to within
your shooting range.</b></font>

86
00:09:38.812 --> 00:09:40.845
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>This might be
a little difficult at first.</b></font>

87
00:09:40.847 --> 00:09:44.082
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- But remember. practice makes perfect.
- (SPEAKING FINNISH)</b></font>

88
00:09:46.886 --> 00:09:48.620
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(CONTINUES TALKING)</b></font>

89
00:10:37.003 --> 00:10:38.302
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(GUN FIRES)</b></font>

90
00:10:49.983 --> 00:10:51.382
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(ENGINE STALLING)</b></font>

91
00:10:58.158 --> 00:10:59.424
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SPEAKING FINNISH)</b></font>

92
00:11:01.394 --> 00:11:02.760
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(ENGINE STARTS)</b></font>

93
00:12:01.321 --> 00:12:02.453
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(GRUNTING)</b></font>

94
00:12:08.328 --> 00:12:09.527
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SPEAKING FINNISH)</b></font>

95
00:12:35.522 --> 00:12:37.155
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SPEAKING FINNISH)</b></font>

96
00:14:14.120 --> 00:14:16.420
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(INDISTINCT TALKING)</b></font>

97
00:14:28.067 --> 00:14:29.600
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Sir.
- John.</b></font>

98
00:14:31.004 --> 00:14:32.336
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What's our ETA?</b></font>

99
00:14:32.338 --> 00:14:34.105
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Forty-five miles.</b></font>

100
00:14:34.107 --> 00:14:35.373
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We just started our descent.</b></font>

101
00:14:35.375 --> 00:14:38.542
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Excellent. I'll tell POTUS.</b></font>

102
00:14:38.544 --> 00:14:40.544
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Oh. and try not to rock
the boat on the way down.</b></font>

103
00:14:40.546 --> 00:14:43.506
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- You know how he hates to spill his coffee.
- (CHUCKLES) Okay.</b></font>

104
00:14:48.554 --> 00:14:49.554
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SIGHS)</b></font>

105
00:14:53.293 --> 00:14:55.026
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- (BEEPING)
- MAN: Oh. shit!</b></font>

106
00:14:55.028 --> 00:14:56.994
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Joe. you got this?
- Affirmative.</b></font>

107
00:14:56.996 --> 00:14:59.497
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- What's going on?
- Someone is targeting us with a SAM.</b></font>

108
00:14:59.499 --> 00:15:02.366
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Holy shit! F-18 escort is reporting
the same. They're lit up too.</b></font>

109
00:15:02.368 --> 00:15:04.168
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Joe. engage
countermeasures now.</b></font>

110
00:15:04.170 --> 00:15:05.570
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- The counters won't engage.
- What?</b></font>

111
00:15:05.571 --> 00:15:07.338
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>JOE: Something is jamming us.
It's like...</b></font>

112
00:15:07.340 --> 00:15:08.940
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- (ALARM BEEPS)
- Whoa. I've lost power.</b></font>

113
00:15:08.942 --> 00:15:11.025
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Jesus Christ!</b></font>

114
00:15:11.026 --> 00:15:13.109
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>All stations. initiate emergency
evacuation procedure.</b></font>

115
00:15:13.112 --> 00:15:15.396
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The President is under attack.</b></font>

116
00:15:15.397 --> 00:15:17.917
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I repeat. emergency evacuation.
The President is under attack.</b></font>

117
00:15:19.152 --> 00:15:20.618
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(BEEPING)</b></font>

118
00:15:21.688 --> 00:15:24.055
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What the hell is going on?</b></font>

119
00:15:24.057 --> 00:15:25.489
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We've got to get you
out of here. Mr. President.</b></font>

120
00:15:25.491 --> 00:15:27.625
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- What about my shoe?
- Forget your damn shoe!</b></font>

121
00:15:27.627 --> 00:15:29.527
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- (STAFF CLAMORING)
- Go. go. go!</b></font>

122
00:15:37.236 --> 00:15:38.970
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Otis. what's going on?</b></font>

123
00:15:38.972 --> 00:15:40.972
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're getting off
this plane. Mr. President.</b></font>

124
00:15:45.178 --> 00:15:47.545
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'll take it from here.
Get the man on the ground.</b></font>

125
00:15:47.547 --> 00:15:49.547
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- MAN: Roger that.
- Are we under attack?</b></font>

126
00:15:49.549 --> 00:15:52.249
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'll find you and pick you up.
Mr. President.</b></font>

127
00:15:52.251 --> 00:15:54.685
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- You'll find what...
- See you on the ground.</b></font>

128
00:15:54.687 --> 00:15:56.387
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No. Morris... Wait!</b></font>

129
00:15:59.158 --> 00:16:00.358
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Morris!</b></font>

130
00:16:06.099 --> 00:16:08.265
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- What about the crew?
- Our concern is the President.</b></font>

131
00:16:08.267 --> 00:16:10.001
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Get out now!
- OTIS: Go!</b></font>

132
00:16:12.038 --> 00:16:13.671
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Clay. jump. go!</b></font>

133
00:16:20.046 --> 00:16:23.047
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>There's something wrong. sir. I
don't see any parachutes opening.</b></font>

134
00:16:23.783 --> 00:16:25.116
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(GRUNTS)</b></font>

135
00:16:56.682 --> 00:16:58.516
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(EXPLODING)</b></font>

136
00:17:39.459 --> 00:17:40.758
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(AIRCRAFT DESCENDING QUICKLY)</b></font>

137
00:18:04.817 --> 00:18:06.617
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SCREAMING)</b></font>

138
00:18:25.471 --> 00:18:26.637
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(INHALING SHARPLY)</b></font>

139
00:18:56.769 --> 00:18:58.836
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The Air Force One
mayday was verified.</b></font>

140
00:18:58.838 --> 00:19:01.238
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>the evacuation protocol
was clearly triggered.</b></font>

141
00:19:01.240 --> 00:19:03.240
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and the POTUS escape pod seems
to have been jettisoned.</b></font>

142
00:19:03.242 --> 00:19:04.375
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Occupants?</b></font>

143
00:19:04.377 --> 00:19:05.776
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- One.
- I see.</b></font>

144
00:19:05.778 --> 00:19:07.878
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And then we lost everything.
all coms. radar profile.</b></font>

145
00:19:07.880 --> 00:19:09.813
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>cell phone signals. gone.</b></font>

146
00:19:10.783 --> 00:19:13.184
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(INDISTINCT TALKING)</b></font>

147
00:19:13.186 --> 00:19:15.719
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Mr. Vice President. I want
to introduce Fred Herbert.</b></font>

148
00:19:15.721 --> 00:19:19.290
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Fred is our longest serving field
operative the CIA has ever had.</b></font>

149
00:19:19.292 --> 00:19:21.559
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We finally convinced him
to come back to Langley.</b></font>

150
00:19:21.561 --> 00:19:23.761
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He now heads
our terrorist Intel unit.</b></font>

151
00:19:23.763 --> 00:19:26.697
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>General. if you would start to
fill Fred in on our known knowns.</b></font>

152
00:19:26.699 --> 00:19:29.433
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Mr. Herbert. sir.</b></font>

153
00:19:29.435 --> 00:19:33.404
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Thirty-six minutes ago. we got an evac
distress signal from Air Force One.</b></font>

154
00:19:33.406 --> 00:19:35.573
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We lost coms
immediately thereafter.</b></font>

155
00:19:35.575 --> 00:19:39.376
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>At T minus 32. Air Force One</b></font>

156
00:19:39.378 --> 00:19:42.880
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and its entire fighter escort
fell off the grid.</b></font>

157
00:19:42.882 --> 00:19:46.817
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>They were over Finland. en route
to Helsinki for a pre-G8 summit.</b></font>

158
00:19:48.287 --> 00:19:50.487
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Sir...</b></font>

159
00:19:50.489 --> 00:19:53.357
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We think this is the most serious
terrorist action since 9/11.</b></font>

160
00:19:53.359 --> 00:19:55.826
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Just a minute here.
just to be clear.</b></font>

161
00:19:55.828 --> 00:19:58.395
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>For all we know.
this was a mechanical failure.</b></font>

162
00:19:58.397 --> 00:20:00.231
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>On five planes.
simultaneously?</b></font>

163
00:20:00.233 --> 00:20:02.533
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- One explodes. takes out the others.
- That's a stretch.</b></font>

164
00:20:02.535 --> 00:20:05.269
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Well. any explanation
is a stretch.</b></font>

165
00:20:05.271 --> 00:20:07.905
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Right now. I'm saying we don't
want to rush to conclusions.</b></font>

166
00:20:07.907 --> 00:20:09.707
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It was a terrorist action.</b></font>

167
00:20:09.709 --> 00:20:11.642
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>employing
a five to 10 man unit.</b></font>

168
00:20:11.644 --> 00:20:13.811
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>They have money.</b></font>

169
00:20:13.812 --> 00:20:15.979
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>They used Chinese-made. shoulder-mounted
surface-to-air missiles.</b></font>

170
00:20:15.982 --> 00:20:17.815
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and they had a guy
on the inside.</b></font>

171
00:20:17.817 --> 00:20:19.383
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Well. how the hell
could you know that?</b></font>

172
00:20:19.384 --> 00:20:20.950
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Well. they had money.
they had to buy the hardware.</b></font>

173
00:20:20.953 --> 00:20:22.987
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It was a five to 10 man unit.</b></font>

174
00:20:22.989 --> 00:20:25.856
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>How do you think they transported
and simultaneously fired the SAMs?</b></font>

175
00:20:25.858 --> 00:20:28.492
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Shoulder-mounted SAMs can't
reach passenger jet altitude.</b></font>

176
00:20:28.494 --> 00:20:30.761
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>They can.</b></font>

177
00:20:30.763 --> 00:20:33.497
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>If the plane is on its
landing trajectory.</b></font>

178
00:20:33.499 --> 00:20:35.466
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and if the point of firing</b></font>

179
00:20:35.468 --> 00:20:37.668
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>is at a higher
than usual altitude.</b></font>

180
00:20:37.670 --> 00:20:40.154
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>like the side of a mountain...</b></font>

181
00:20:40.155 --> 00:20:42.639
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But Air Force One was fitted with
every countermeasure known to man.</b></font>

182
00:20:42.642 --> 00:20:45.843
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>That's the job of the guy on
the inside. to disable them.</b></font>

183
00:20:45.845 --> 00:20:48.746
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Wait. he used a jammer.
an EMP device?</b></font>

184
00:20:48.748 --> 00:20:50.981
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Or a screwdriver
and a pair of pliers.</b></font>

185
00:20:50.983 --> 00:20:53.851
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What about getting a man
on Air Force One?</b></font>

186
00:20:53.853 --> 00:20:56.320
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>How could they penetrate
security that tight?</b></font>

187
00:20:56.322 --> 00:20:57.488
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Same way they always do.</b></font>

188
00:20:58.391 --> 00:20:59.957
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Money.</b></font>

189
00:20:59.959 --> 00:21:01.558
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>sex.</b></font>

190
00:21:01.560 --> 00:21:02.693
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>or God.</b></font>

191
00:21:03.696 --> 00:21:05.029
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Any suggestions?</b></font>

192
00:21:06.699 --> 00:21:08.499
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>There's only one thing left.</b></font>

193
00:21:08.501 --> 00:21:09.867
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Find the President.</b></font>

194
00:21:09.869 --> 00:21:11.949
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>kill the sons of bitches
who are after him...</b></font>

195
00:21:12.905 --> 00:21:13.937
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Bring him home.</b></font>

196
00:21:23.983 --> 00:21:25.516
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(GRUNTING)</b></font>

197
00:21:33.092 --> 00:21:34.525
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(GRUNTS)</b></font>

198
00:21:38.464 --> 00:21:39.863
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(PANTING)</b></font>

199
00:21:40.733 --> 00:21:41.965
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(GROANING)</b></font>

200
00:21:54.413 --> 00:21:57.781
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>This is Agent Echo-Mike. calling
all agents on the ground.</b></font>

201
00:21:59.352 --> 00:22:01.018
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Respond immediately.</b></font>

202
00:22:02.621 --> 00:22:05.622
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I repeat. Agent Echo-Mike.</b></font>

203
00:22:06.792 --> 00:22:08.659
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Is anyone receiving?</b></font>

204
00:22:10.596 --> 00:22:12.062
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No one.</b></font>

205
00:22:12.064 --> 00:22:14.131
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Glad to hear it. over and out.</b></font>

206
00:22:19.972 --> 00:22:20.972
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(BEEPS)</b></font>

207
00:22:21.974 --> 00:22:23.907
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Angel is down.</b></font>

208
00:22:23.909 --> 00:22:25.876
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- We're good to go.
- (BEEPS)</b></font>

209
00:22:41.160 --> 00:22:42.960
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(STEADY BEEPING)</b></font>

210
00:22:57.476 --> 00:22:58.609
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(BANGING)</b></font>

211
00:23:23.969 --> 00:23:25.202
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(POUNDING)</b></font>

212
00:24:04.610 --> 00:24:07.077
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(MUMBLING)</b></font>

213
00:24:11.183 --> 00:24:12.183
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(BEEPS)</b></font>

214
00:24:22.895 --> 00:24:26.864
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>AUTOMATED VOICE: Please stay
inside. help is on the way.</b></font>

215
00:24:26.866 --> 00:24:31.034
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Do not exit the rescue pod
under any circumstance.</b></font>

216
00:24:33.272 --> 00:24:37.174
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Please stay inside.
help is on the way.</b></font>

217
00:24:38.077 --> 00:24:39.877
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Do not exit the rescue pod...</b></font>

218
00:24:44.717 --> 00:24:46.216
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>PRESIDENT: Show yourself!</b></font>

219
00:24:55.794 --> 00:24:57.728
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Come out!</b></font>

220
00:25:06.138 --> 00:25:07.704
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Please...</b></font>

221
00:25:07.706 --> 00:25:09.206
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(BOW STRING TWANGING)</b></font>

222
00:25:24.256 --> 00:25:26.590
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(OSKARI SPEAKING FINNISH)</b></font>

223
00:25:30.763 --> 00:25:33.130
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What language is this?</b></font>

224
00:25:33.132 --> 00:25:35.198
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Can you show yourself. please?</b></font>

225
00:25:37.903 --> 00:25:40.103
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>OSKARI: From what planet
are you from?</b></font>

226
00:25:42.708 --> 00:25:43.907
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I am from Earth.</b></font>

227
00:25:43.909 --> 00:25:46.009
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Is this some kid
I'm talking to?</b></font>

228
00:25:47.112 --> 00:25:49.212
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>OSKARI: Do you come in peace?</b></font>

229
00:25:49.214 --> 00:25:50.714
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Yes. (SCOFFS)</b></font>

230
00:25:51.984 --> 00:25:54.117
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Yes. I...
I come in peace.</b></font>

231
00:25:54.119 --> 00:25:55.919
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Most definitely. yes. I...
- (CLANGING)</b></font>

232
00:25:55.921 --> 00:25:57.988
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Wait. wait. don't hang...</b></font>

233
00:25:57.990 --> 00:26:00.190
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>"Don't hang up."
What's wrong with me?</b></font>

234
00:26:00.192 --> 00:26:01.325
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SIGHS)</b></font>

235
00:26:03.228 --> 00:26:06.163
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Look. could you please
just come out?</b></font>

236
00:26:12.871 --> 00:26:15.138
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Whoa. whoa. kid. hey!</b></font>

237
00:26:15.140 --> 00:26:18.275
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Can we. um.
lose the bow and arrow?</b></font>

238
00:26:19.011 --> 00:26:20.177
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Who are you?</b></font>

239
00:26:21.947 --> 00:26:23.880
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You don't recognize me?</b></font>

240
00:26:26.852 --> 00:26:28.919
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm William Allen Moore.</b></font>

241
00:26:29.989 --> 00:26:31.121
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>the President</b></font>

242
00:26:32.858 --> 00:26:34.891
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>of the United States.</b></font>

243
00:26:35.294 --> 00:26:36.326
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Prove it.</b></font>

244
00:26:41.233 --> 00:26:42.299
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SIGHS)</b></font>

245
00:26:46.739 --> 00:26:47.871
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Stay.</b></font>

246
00:27:13.232 --> 00:27:14.331
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Are you hurt?</b></font>

247
00:27:14.333 --> 00:27:15.899
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No.</b></font>

248
00:27:16.935 --> 00:27:18.802
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I am lost.</b></font>

249
00:27:18.804 --> 00:27:20.704
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And I could use your help.</b></font>

250
00:27:21.840 --> 00:27:23.306
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Do you have a phone?</b></font>

251
00:27:24.943 --> 00:27:26.810
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No. no. no. no.
a real phone.</b></font>

252
00:27:28.814 --> 00:27:30.747
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Or is your house close by.</b></font>

253
00:27:30.749 --> 00:27:32.282
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>a town. small village?</b></font>

254
00:27:34.853 --> 00:27:36.086
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Where did you come from?</b></font>

255
00:27:36.088 --> 00:27:37.454
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I mean.
there must be something.</b></font>

256
00:27:37.456 --> 00:27:39.416
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I mean. did you just pop up
out of the ground?</b></font>

257
00:27:41.460 --> 00:27:42.826
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(CLAMORING)</b></font>

258
00:27:42.828 --> 00:27:44.227
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Vice President.</b></font>

259
00:27:45.898 --> 00:27:48.065
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>we have located
the rescue pod tracker.</b></font>

260
00:27:51.837 --> 00:27:54.304
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Sir. the situation
is under control.</b></font>

261
00:27:56.909 --> 00:27:58.809
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>PILOT: This is Genik 1
to Command.</b></font>

262
00:27:58.811 --> 00:28:01.044
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We have confirmed signal from
the President's escape pod.</b></font>

263
00:28:01.046 --> 00:28:02.446
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We are closing in on it now.</b></font>

264
00:28:03.949 --> 00:28:06.817
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>ETA. one minute.</b></font>

265
00:28:06.819 --> 00:28:09.786
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Copy that. Genik 1.
secure the President.</b></font>

266
00:28:10.189 --> 00:28:11.888
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(BARKING)</b></font>

267
00:28:26.071 --> 00:28:27.738
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Shh.
- (WHIMPERS)</b></font>

268
00:28:30.809 --> 00:28:32.275
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(BEEPING)</b></font>

269
00:28:48.827 --> 00:28:50.794
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(WIND WHOOSHING)</b></font>

270
00:29:01.507 --> 00:29:03.940
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>PILOT:  This is Genik 1.
the pod is not here.</b></font>

271
00:29:04.810 --> 00:29:06.877
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- What?
- Repeat that. Genik 1.</b></font>

272
00:29:06.879 --> 00:29:09.146
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We did not copy. over.</b></font>

273
00:29:09.148 --> 00:29:11.948
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Uh. the homing beacon and the escape
pod must have separated. sir.</b></font>

274
00:29:11.950 --> 00:29:14.217
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I say again.
the President is not here.</b></font>

275
00:29:14.987 --> 00:29:16.253
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>God in heaven!</b></font>

276
00:29:18.190 --> 00:29:21.491
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Genik 1. return to base.
await further instructions.</b></font>

277
00:29:22.995 --> 00:29:24.327
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Over and out.</b></font>

278
00:29:24.329 --> 00:29:26.429
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>PILOT: Roger that. Genik 1 out.</b></font>

279
00:29:29.501 --> 00:29:31.434
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I apologize. sir.</b></font>

280
00:29:31.436 --> 00:29:34.337
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're telling me
we lost our President</b></font>

281
00:29:34.339 --> 00:29:36.973
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>like you lose
a set of car keys.</b></font>

282
00:29:38.477 --> 00:29:42.012
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>This is the most powerful nation
in the history of the planet.</b></font>

283
00:29:42.948 --> 00:29:43.948
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Look at me!</b></font>

284
00:29:45.884 --> 00:29:47.484
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>This is America.</b></font>

285
00:29:47.486 --> 00:29:51.488
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and as Vice President
of this great nation.</b></font>

286
00:29:51.490 --> 00:29:55.992
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I am commanding you
to sort this shit out!</b></font>

287
00:30:00.132 --> 00:30:01.932
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(HELICOPTER APPROACHING)</b></font>

288
00:30:08.106 --> 00:30:10.040
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Interestingly. my department</b></font>

289
00:30:10.042 --> 00:30:12.275
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>has registered
precisely no chatter</b></font>

290
00:30:12.277 --> 00:30:14.878
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>about an action of this sort.</b></font>

291
00:30:14.880 --> 00:30:17.280
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Which leaves us with
the trickiest possibility.</b></font>

292
00:30:18.350 --> 00:30:20.183
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The lone wolf.
the jackal.</b></font>

293
00:30:20.185 --> 00:30:21.718
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>who got his own agenda.</b></font>

294
00:30:21.719 --> 00:30:23.599
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>affiliated to
no particular cause.</b></font>

295
00:30:24.156 --> 00:30:26.056
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Extremely hard to track.</b></font>

296
00:30:26.058 --> 00:30:28.425
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>impossible to predict.</b></font>

297
00:30:28.427 --> 00:30:30.260
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And finally we have
the central question...</b></font>

298
00:30:30.262 --> 00:30:32.028
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What do they actually want?</b></font>

299
00:30:32.030 --> 00:30:33.997
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What is the purpose
of their...</b></font>

300
00:30:35.567 --> 00:30:37.033
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>...operation?</b></font>

301
00:30:37.035 --> 00:30:39.202
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Well. that we do know.</b></font>

302
00:30:39.204 --> 00:30:40.637
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Their intention was
to assassinate</b></font>

303
00:30:40.639 --> 00:30:42.038
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>the President
of the United States.</b></font>

304
00:30:42.040 --> 00:30:44.274
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm not sure.</b></font>

305
00:30:44.275 --> 00:30:46.509
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What. there might be another intention
behind blowing up his plane?</b></font>

306
00:30:46.511 --> 00:30:48.391
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Big game hunting
never got any bigger.</b></font>

307
00:30:53.018 --> 00:30:55.385
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Based on our knowledge
at this moment in time.</b></font>

308
00:30:55.387 --> 00:30:57.354
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>the President
is not assassinated.</b></font>

309
00:30:57.356 --> 00:31:00.624
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We do know that the evac was triggered.
Maybe that's what they wanted.</b></font>

310
00:31:00.626 --> 00:31:02.459
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>To capture him.
to take him alive.</b></font>

311
00:31:02.461 --> 00:31:05.428
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>God damn it. so they can show off
their trophy and make demands.</b></font>

312
00:31:09.468 --> 00:31:11.368
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Kazim.
- Ready.</b></font>

313
00:31:11.370 --> 00:31:12.469
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(LOCK BEEPS OPEN)</b></font>

314
00:31:19.645 --> 00:31:22.325
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Where is he?
- AUTOMATED VOICE: Help is on the way...</b></font>

315
00:31:24.082 --> 00:31:25.582
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>OSKARI: You're lucky.</b></font>

316
00:31:25.584 --> 00:31:27.017
