<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What are you talking about?</b></font>

638
00:53:07.751 --> 00:53:09.985
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Well. I spoke
to my taxidermist</b></font>

639
00:53:09.987 --> 00:53:14.389
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>about some logistics of
dealing with a human cadaver.</b></font>

640
00:53:14.391 --> 00:53:18.360
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And apparently. if I'm going
to stuff him and mount him.</b></font>

641
00:53:18.362 --> 00:53:20.629
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>it's best that the body
is as fresh as possible.</b></font>

642
00:53:24.235 --> 00:53:26.602
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- You're gonna stuff him?
- (CHUCKLES)</b></font>

643
00:53:26.604 --> 00:53:28.724
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What else should one do
with a hunting trophy?</b></font>

644
00:53:31.442 --> 00:53:32.641
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're insane.</b></font>

645
00:53:34.712 --> 00:53:36.662
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're a very wealthy man.</b></font>

646
00:53:36.663 --> 00:53:39.023
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I just transferred $10 million
to the agreed bank account.</b></font>

647
00:53:39.416 --> 00:53:40.682
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SPEAKING ARABIC)</b></font>

648
00:53:44.655 --> 00:53:46.375
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- MAN: Come on!
- (GRUNTING)</b></font>

649
00:53:47.691 --> 00:53:49.571
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Get in the box.
- PRESIDENT: What?</b></font>

650
00:53:49.994 --> 00:53:51.526
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Get in the box.</b></font>

651
00:54:08.612 --> 00:54:10.445
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My apologies.</b></font>

652
00:54:10.447 --> 00:54:11.813
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>First class was full.</b></font>

653
00:54:18.989 --> 00:54:21.023
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Where the hell
are our Navy SEALs?</b></font>

654
00:54:21.025 --> 00:54:24.593
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>MC-130 is in the air. They're
ready for a helo drop.</b></font>

655
00:54:24.595 --> 00:54:26.555
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>but they're still
30 minutes out. madam.</b></font>

656
00:54:27.998 --> 00:54:30.666
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>If anybody has a clue how
to get us out of this mess.</b></font>

657
00:54:30.668 --> 00:54:32.428
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>now would be a good time
to speak up.</b></font>

658
00:54:54.692 --> 00:54:55.824
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Who the hell is that?</b></font>

659
00:55:14.945 --> 00:55:16.912
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SPEAKING FINNISH)</b></font>

660
00:56:03.460 --> 00:56:05.560
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- What are you doing here?
- Now I know.</b></font>

661
00:56:05.562 --> 00:56:06.862
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Know what?</b></font>

662
00:56:06.864 --> 00:56:08.964
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The forest did give me
something.</b></font>

663
00:56:08.966 --> 00:56:11.183
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What?</b></font>

664
00:56:11.184 --> 00:56:13.401
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Do you know what is even bigger
than the king of the forest?</b></font>

665
00:56:13.404 --> 00:56:14.703
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- No.
- It's you.</b></font>

666
00:56:14.705 --> 00:56:16.905
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I must take you to my dad.</b></font>

667
00:56:16.907 --> 00:56:18.774
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The President
of the United States.</b></font>

668
00:56:23.147 --> 00:56:25.147
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The load is slowing us down.</b></font>

669
00:56:25.149 --> 00:56:26.848
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>This whole area
is gonna be crawling</b></font>

670
00:56:26.850 --> 00:56:29.451
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>with US Special Forces
any moment now.</b></font>

671
00:56:29.453 --> 00:56:31.920
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I just bagged the biggest
prize on the planet.</b></font>

672
00:56:31.922 --> 00:56:33.455
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Try to enjoy it with me.</b></font>

673
00:56:33.457 --> 00:56:36.658
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SPEAKING ARABIC)</b></font>

674
00:56:36.660 --> 00:56:39.628
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- What did he say?
- We've got a stowaway.</b></font>

675
00:56:45.536 --> 00:56:47.936
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It's that damn kid!</b></font>

676
00:56:47.938 --> 00:56:50.605
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Shake him off.
Return him back to his forest.</b></font>

677
00:56:52.676 --> 00:56:54.509
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>PRESIDENT: Ranger. Ranger. look out!</b></font>

678
00:56:54.511 --> 00:56:56.478
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(OSKARI SCREAMING)</b></font>

679
00:56:58.982 --> 00:57:00.902
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hang on. they're trying
to knock you off.</b></font>

680
00:57:04.455 --> 00:57:06.575
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>HAZAR: Knock him off.
Use it like a wrecking ball.</b></font>

681
00:57:10.928 --> 00:57:12.794
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>PRESIDENT: Ranger.
you shouldn't be here.</b></font>

682
00:57:12.796 --> 00:57:14.896
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Don't worry. Mr. President.</b></font>

683
00:57:14.898 --> 00:57:16.498
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- I will save you.
- Hang on!</b></font>

684
00:57:17.668 --> 00:57:20.635
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Ranger! Ranger! Ranger!</b></font>

685
00:57:22.539 --> 00:57:24.172
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Are you all right?</b></font>

686
00:57:25.142 --> 00:57:26.142
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>OSKARI: Get off!</b></font>

687
00:57:28.045 --> 00:57:30.812
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- You have to jump!
- Oh. hell. no!</b></font>

688
00:57:30.814 --> 00:57:32.948
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Now. shoot the boy. shoot him!
Shoot him!</b></font>

689
00:57:50.133 --> 00:57:51.633
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>PRESIDENT: No! No!</b></font>

690
00:57:52.870 --> 00:57:55.103
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I got you! Come on!
Grab the strap!</b></font>

691
00:57:57.841 --> 00:57:59.007
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'll cut you loose.</b></font>

692
00:57:59.009 --> 00:58:01.843
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No. no. no.
that's not a good idea.</b></font>

693
00:58:01.845 --> 00:58:05.080
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Close the lid.
- This is not a good idea!</b></font>

694
00:58:11.855 --> 00:58:12.954
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No!</b></font>

695
00:58:14.057 --> 00:58:17.025
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hazar. get me
on the ground. now!</b></font>

696
00:58:22.699 --> 00:58:23.999
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(PANTING)</b></font>

697
00:58:29.206 --> 00:58:32.040
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- (GROANING)
- President. you okay?</b></font>

698
00:58:32.042 --> 00:58:35.010
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(GROANING) How the hell
did I survive that?</b></font>

699
00:58:35.012 --> 00:58:37.279
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And where are my soldiers?</b></font>

700
00:58:37.281 --> 00:58:39.147
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm the commander
of the biggest. bad-ass.</b></font>

701
00:58:39.149 --> 00:58:41.316
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>ass-kicking armed forces
on the planet.</b></font>

702
00:58:41.318 --> 00:58:43.718
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Why aren't they scouring this
wilderness trying to rescue me?</b></font>

703
00:58:44.087 --> 00:58:45.320
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>There's no one to help us.</b></font>

704
00:58:46.256 --> 00:58:49.591
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Not my dad. and not your army.</b></font>

705
00:58:49.593 --> 00:58:51.159
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We have to help ourselves.</b></font>

706
00:58:52.062 --> 00:58:53.562
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Instead of looking tough.</b></font>

707
00:58:55.632 --> 00:58:57.299
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>we have to be tough.</b></font>

708
00:58:57.301 --> 00:58:58.301
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Right.</b></font>

709
00:58:59.236 --> 00:59:00.236
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Okay.</b></font>

710
00:59:00.938 --> 00:59:02.170
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Oh! Oskari. look out!</b></font>

711
00:59:06.076 --> 00:59:08.009
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(MACHINE GUN FIRING)</b></font>

712
00:59:12.849 --> 00:59:15.369
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- This your idea of being tough?
- No.</b></font>

713
00:59:16.053 --> 00:59:17.218
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>This is.</b></font>

714
00:59:17.921 --> 00:59:19.654
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No. Oskari. no. No!</b></font>

715
00:59:19.656 --> 00:59:20.922
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SCREAMING)</b></font>

716
00:59:31.268 --> 00:59:33.168
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What the hell are they doing?</b></font>

717
00:59:34.338 --> 00:59:36.805
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SCREAMING)</b></font>

718
00:59:48.051 --> 00:59:50.752
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>PRESIDENT: (SCREAMING) We're gonna die!</b></font>

719
01:00:42.739 --> 01:00:44.706
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(GROANING)</b></font>

720
01:00:51.915 --> 01:00:53.181
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You think we lost 'em?</b></font>

721
01:00:54.351 --> 01:00:55.417
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I hope so.</b></font>

722
01:01:08.131 --> 01:01:09.230
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Look.</b></font>

723
01:01:22.112 --> 01:01:25.146
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Is that what I think it is?</b></font>

724
01:01:25.148 --> 01:01:29.184
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Affirmative. We just found the
crash site of Air Force One.</b></font>

725
01:01:29.186 --> 01:01:31.986
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Give those GPS coordinates to the SEALs.
- MAN: Yes. sir.</b></font>

726
01:01:33.423 --> 01:01:35.256
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(INDISTINCT RADIO CONVERSATION)</b></font>

727
01:01:48.939 --> 01:01:50.071
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(CELL PHONE BEEPS)</b></font>

728
01:01:56.480 --> 01:01:57.879
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Shit.</b></font>

729
01:02:02.052 --> 01:02:03.752
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My dad is waiting for me.</b></font>

730
01:02:05.255 --> 01:02:06.855
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We've got only one hour.</b></font>

731
01:02:08.191 --> 01:02:09.324
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Can you swim?</b></font>

732
01:02:10.761 --> 01:02:13.128
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Of course I can.</b></font>

733
01:02:13.130 --> 01:02:15.029
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- They're back.
- (HELICOPTER APPROACHING)</b></font>

734
01:02:16.833 --> 01:02:18.199
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We have to get in that plane.</b></font>

735
01:02:18.201 --> 01:02:19.234
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Let's go.</b></font>

736
01:02:43.560 --> 01:02:45.226
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Switch to thermal imaging.</b></font>

737
01:02:49.366 --> 01:02:50.498
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>They're going in.</b></font>

738
01:02:53.937 --> 01:02:55.497
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- (BREATHING HEAVILY)
- Great.</b></font>

739
01:02:56.072 --> 01:02:57.806
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Stick with me.</b></font>

740
01:02:57.808 --> 01:02:59.208
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Oh. Jesus.
- Oh!</b></font>

741
01:03:01.178 --> 01:03:03.411
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Looks like the upper deck
may be clean.</b></font>

742
01:03:03.413 --> 01:03:04.846
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Come on. swim with me.</b></font>

743
01:03:18.495 --> 01:03:20.328
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(PANTING)</b></font>

744
01:03:44.321 --> 01:03:45.321
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Okay.</b></font>

745
01:03:47.157 --> 01:03:48.857
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We're gonna be okay now.</b></font>

746
01:03:50.427 --> 01:03:53.361
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>All we have to do
is wait for the army.</b></font>

747
01:03:53.363 --> 01:03:55.029
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>OSKARI: But...</b></font>

748
01:03:55.031 --> 01:03:56.464
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Don't worry. (GROANS)</b></font>

749
01:03:59.302 --> 01:04:01.035
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'll get you to your father.</b></font>

750
01:04:02.339 --> 01:04:03.371
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SIGHS)</b></font>

751
01:04:10.380 --> 01:04:11.913
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SIGHING)</b></font>

752
01:04:11.915 --> 01:04:13.147
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(THUDDING)</b></font>

753
01:04:23.093 --> 01:04:24.425
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(METAL CREAKING)</b></font>

754
01:04:25.428 --> 01:04:27.595
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What is that?</b></font>

755
01:04:27.597 --> 01:04:29.631
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Well. if it's not the cavalry.
it can't be good.</b></font>

756
01:04:31.968 --> 01:04:33.668
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(FOOTSTEPS)</b></font>

757
01:04:37.974 --> 01:04:39.908
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(METAL GROANING)</b></font>

758
01:04:45.615 --> 01:04:47.248
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Do you think they're gone?</b></font>

759
01:04:47.250 --> 01:04:48.516
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(EXPLODING)</b></font>

760
01:05:04.167 --> 01:05:06.067
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>HAZAR: What have we here?</b></font>

761
01:05:16.146 --> 01:05:17.545
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Oskari! Oskari!</b></font>

762
01:05:17.547 --> 01:05:20.548
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Mr. President.
please accept my apologies.</b></font>

763
01:05:20.550 --> 01:05:22.183
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My mission
was to take you alive.</b></font>

764
01:05:22.185 --> 01:05:24.152
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>but now I have no choice
but to kill you.</b></font>

765
01:05:24.154 --> 01:05:25.453
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Your mission?</b></font>

766
01:05:25.455 --> 01:05:27.622
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>HAZAR: You were going
to be held captive.</b></font>

767
01:05:27.624 --> 01:05:30.491
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>filmed. documenting every
moment of your imprisonment.</b></font>

768
01:05:31.561 --> 01:05:34.228
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and after seven days
you would be martyred.</b></font>

769
01:05:34.230 --> 01:05:36.030
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The images would horrify
the world.</b></font>

770
01:05:36.032 --> 01:05:39.534
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and the world would know the
war on terror is not over.</b></font>

771
01:05:39.536 --> 01:05:42.554
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What the hell
kind of terrorist are you?</b></font>

772
01:05:42.555 --> 01:05:46.195
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>If it's any consolation to you before you die.
Mr. President. I'm actually on your side.</b></font>

773
01:05:47.110 --> 01:05:48.230
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And what does that mean?</b></font>

774
01:05:48.712 --> 01:05:49.752
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>That's a long story.</b></font>

775
01:05:50.680 --> 01:05:52.146
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Some other time.</b></font>

776
01:05:52.148 --> 01:05:53.247
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm done here.</b></font>

777
01:05:54.317 --> 01:05:55.416
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Yes. you are.</b></font>

778
01:06:04.627 --> 01:06:06.467
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Huh. Well. I know
how that feels.</b></font>

779
01:06:22.012 --> 01:06:23.511
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Oh. God! (SCREAMING)</b></font>

780
01:06:27.717 --> 01:06:29.550
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SCREAMING)</b></font>

781
01:07:01.351 --> 01:07:02.617
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(CHOKING)</b></font>

782
01:07:04.587 --> 01:07:06.421
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- (OSKARI MIMICS DEER CALL)
- What's that?</b></font>

783
01:07:09.125 --> 01:07:10.491
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>That was a deer.</b></font>

784
01:07:12.595 --> 01:07:14.529
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- You little brat.
- (GUN CLICKING)</b></font>

785
01:07:24.607 --> 01:07:26.174
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You gotta cock it...</b></font>

786
01:07:26.176 --> 01:07:27.241
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(GUN FIRING)</b></font>

787
01:07:43.393 --> 01:07:44.559
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We have to get out of here.</b></font>

788
01:07:46.262 --> 01:07:47.662
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(BEEPING SOFTLY)</b></font>

789
01:07:48.698 --> 01:07:50.338
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- We can swim out.
- (GUNFIRE)</b></font>

790
01:07:54.871 --> 01:07:56.637
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I don't think so.</b></font>

791
01:07:56.639 --> 01:07:58.473
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>There is one other thing
we can try.</b></font>

792
01:07:58.475 --> 01:07:59.574
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Come on.</b></font>

793
01:08:01.311 --> 01:08:03.611
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>She's gonna blow! Go now!</b></font>

794
01:08:03.613 --> 01:08:05.513
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SPEAKING ARABIC)</b></font>

795
01:08:05.515 --> 01:08:07.115
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(FIRING)
(MAN GROANS)</b></font>

796
01:08:07.851 --> 01:08:09.150
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I said. go now!</b></font>

797
01:08:09.152 --> 01:08:10.751
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(PILOT SPEAKING ARABIC)</b></font>

798
01:08:17.293 --> 01:08:18.459
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Don't worry. President.</b></font>

799
01:08:19.796 --> 01:08:21.462
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I got this.</b></font>

800
01:08:21.464 --> 01:08:23.297
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- (EXHALES) Here we go.
- (EXHALES)</b></font>

801
01:08:45.488 --> 01:08:46.821
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Do you read me now?</b></font>

802
01:09:17.887 --> 01:09:18.887
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(GASPING)</b></font>

803
01:09:32.969 --> 01:09:34.602
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(EXPLODING)</b></font>

804
01:10:07.303 --> 01:10:09.370
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SPEAKING FINNISH)</b></font>

805
01:10:15.678 --> 01:10:16.811
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(THUDDING)</b></font>

806
01:10:18.915 --> 01:10:22.250
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SPEAKING FINNISH)</b></font>

807
01:10:39.936 --> 01:10:41.402
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(KNOCKING ON DOOR)</b></font>

808
01:10:44.574 --> 01:10:47.275
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Get out! Get out of the truck!
Move! I said. move!</b></font>

809
01:10:47.543 --> 01:10:49.610
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Get out!</b></font>

810
01:10:49.612 --> 01:10:52.580
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>All right. clear the area! Let's go!
Come on. move! Go. go. go!</b></font>

811
01:10:53.716 --> 01:10:55.316
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Move straight ahead! Move!</b></font>

812
01:10:55.318 --> 01:10:57.318
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Do not look at me.</b></font>

813
01:10:57.320 --> 01:10:59.820
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>SOLDIER #2: Weapons!
All weapons to the ground now!</b></font>

814
01:10:59.822 --> 01:11:01.756
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Hands behind your back.
- SOLDIER #3: All right. this way.</b></font>

815
01:11:01.758 --> 01:11:04.025
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Move! Get down!
Get down on your knees!</b></font>

816
01:11:04.027 --> 01:11:05.359
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Nobody move!</b></font>

817
01:11:05.361 --> 01:11:07.595
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>SEAL team to base.
we're on the ground.</b></font>

818
01:11:07.597 --> 01:11:10.598
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Looks like the entire lake's
been vaporized.</b></font>

819
01:11:10.600 --> 01:11:11.999
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>GENERAL: Copy that.
(SIGHING)</b></font>

820
01:11:12.001 --> 01:11:14.468
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>There is no way
they could've survived that.</b></font>

821
01:11:16.039 --> 01:11:17.338
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Mr. Vice President. sir.</b></font>

822
01:11:19.075 --> 01:11:21.976
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm sorry. but you have to be
formally sworn in.</b></font>

823
01:11:24.047 --> 01:11:26.814
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Take the office of President
of the United States.</b></font>

824
01:11:30.987 --> 01:11:32.887
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>For my God and country.</b></font>

825
01:11:34.657 --> 01:11:36.824
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I accept.</b></font>

826
01:11:36.826 --> 01:11:39.427
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>SOLDIER: Hurry up!
Move in. over there!</b></font>

827
01:11:39.429 --> 01:11:42.463
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>SOLDIER #2: Copy that. We're not coming
home until we find the President's body.</b></font>

828
01:11:42.465 --> 01:11:44.625
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>GENERAL: (OVER RADIO)
Or what's left of him anyway.</b></font>

829
01:11:44.967 --> 01:11:46.867
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(EXHAUST FIRING)</b></font>

830
01:11:51.541 --> 01:11:53.074
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>SOLDIER: What the hell?</b></font>

831
01:11:53.076 --> 01:11:54.442
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Sir. above. incoming.</b></font>

832
01:11:56.679 --> 01:12:00.548
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Base. we have an unidentified
flying object closing fast.</b></font>

833
01:12:00.550 --> 01:12:01.882
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>you should have
a visual on this.</b></font>

834
01:12:01.884 --> 01:12:03.617
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Streaming now. take a look.</b></font>

835
01:12:13.363 --> 01:12:16.630
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Stay alert.
The object is on the ground.</b></font>

836
01:12:16.632 --> 01:12:18.833
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I say again.
the object is on the ground.</b></font>

837
01:12:20.069 --> 01:12:21.402
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Stay alert.</b></font>

838
01:12:22.772 --> 01:12:24.438
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And I see movement.</b></font>

839
01:12:26.676 --> 01:12:28.709
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(STUTTERING)
I've got a young boy</b></font>

840
01:12:29.612 --> 01:12:30.778
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>with a bow and arrow.</b></font>

841
01:12:35.485 --> 01:12:37.118
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SPEAKING FINNISH)</b></font>

842
01:12:46.896 --> 01:12:48.462
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SPEAKING FINNISH)</b></font>

843
01:12:48.464 --> 01:12:49.497
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Stay where you are.</b></font>

844
01:13:14.757 --> 01:13:17.458
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SPEAKING FINNISH)</b></font>

845
01:13:20.563 --> 01:13:21.829
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You must be Tapio.</b></font>

846
01:13:22.932 --> 01:13:25.733
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Yes.
- I've heard a great deal about you.</b></font>

847
01:13:25.735 --> 01:13:27.535
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I understand
you're a great hunter.</b></font>

848
01:13:28.604 --> 01:13:30.805
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Just so you know. so is he.</b></font>

849
01:13:33.910 --> 01:13:35.910
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You have an amazing son.</b></font>

850
01:13:36.813 --> 01:13:38.846
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Bravest man I've ever met.</b></font>

851
01:13:43.653 --> 01:13:45.019
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SPEAKING FINNISH)</b></font>

852
01:13:51.093 --> 01:13:52.693
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(LAUGHS)</b></font>

853
01:13:57.033 --> 01:13:59.467
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SPEAKING FINNISH)</b></font>

854
01:14:01.804 --> 01:14:03.504
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Good to see you.
Mr. President.</b></font>

855
01:14:03.506 --> 01:14:04.705
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Are you all right?</b></font>

856
01:14:05.174 --> 01:14:07.074
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Well.</b></font>

857
01:14:07.076 --> 01:14:10.711
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>considering I've been
betrayed today. hunted.</b></font>

858
01:14:10.713 --> 01:14:14.114
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>locked in a freezer. ejected
from the same plane twice.</b></font>

859
01:14:14.116 --> 01:14:15.916
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>yeah. I'm...
I'm doing quite well.</b></font>

860
01:14:16.786 --> 01:14:18.219
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Thanks to this young man here.</b></font>

861
01:14:22.625 --> 01:14:25.465
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm proud to serve under
your command. Mr. President.</b></font>

862
01:14:25.761 --> 01:14:27.895
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>SEAL team one reporting.</b></font>

863
01:14:27.897 --> 01:14:30.164
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I've got eyes on the President
and he is secure.</b></font>

864
01:14:30.166 --> 01:14:32.199
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I repeat. the President
is secure.</b></font>

865
01:14:32.201 --> 01:14:33.968
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(CHEERING)</b></font>

866
01:14:49.919 --> 01:14:52.119
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Well. that was
quite a screw-up.</b></font>

867
01:14:53.523 --> 01:14:56.690
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Fifteen years I knew Hazar.</b></font>

868
01:14:56.692 --> 01:14:59.927
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Best and most loyal agent I ever
had. and what did we achieve?</b></font>

869
01:15:01.597 --> 01:15:04.198
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Instead of turning
the President into a martyr.</b></font>

870
01:15:05.701 --> 01:15:07.234
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>we turn him into a hero.</b></font>

871
01:15:10.306 --> 01:15:13.641
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Not to mention. I lost my shot
at the Presidency.</b></font>

872
01:15:17.013 --> 01:15:19.813
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I've got one question for you.
friend. one question only.</b></font>

873
01:15:20.917 --> 01:15:23.050
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Can it get back to us?</b></font>

874
01:15:23.052 --> 01:15:24.585
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Can it get back to us?</b></font>

875
01:15:25.221 --> 01:15:26.787
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Well. Vice President.</b></font>

876
01:15:27.323 --> 01:15:28.789
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Morris is dead.</b></font>

877
01:15:29.325 --> 01:15:30.958
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hazar is dead.</b></font>

878
01:15:32.628 --> 01:15:33.928
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>all his men are dead.</b></font>

879
01:15:43.172 --> 01:15:44.705
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And you're dead.</b></font>

880
01:15:46.709 --> 01:15:47.942
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>So.</b></font>

881
01:15:50.112 --> 01:15:51.979
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>in answer to your question.</b></font>

882
01:15:54.250 --> 01:15:56.183
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>getting back to anyone?</b></font>

883
01:15:58.287 --> 01:16:00.754
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I would say. no.</b></font>

884
01:16:04.627 --> 01:16:06.860
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It's not getting back
to anyone.</b></font>

885
01:16:24.981 --> 01:16:27.081
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(INDISTINCT TALKING)</b></font>

886
01:16:40.363 --> 01:16:42.262
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>(SPEAKING FINNISH)</b></font>
